title: Dickinson football player flown to hospital with injury
text:
Dickinson football player flown to hospital with injury Published On: Oct 23 2015 09:41:49 PM CDT Tweet FRIENDSWOOD, Texas - 
A high school football player was flown to a hospital after an injury during Friday's game between Friendswood and Dickinson. 
The injured player was from the visiting Dickinson Gators. 
Witnesses told KPRC 2 the player was hurt after being tackled by a group of players. Quick Clicks
